msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bless.md:9
msgid "# Bless _1st-level enchantment_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bless.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action   \n"
"**Range:** 30 feet   \n"
"**Components:** V, S, M (a sprinkling of holy water)    \n"
"**Duration:** Concentration, up to 1 minute \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bless.md:16
msgid ""
"You bless up to three creatures of your choice within range. Whenever a "
"target makes an attack roll or a saving throw before the spell ends, the "
"target can roll a d4 and add the number rolled to the attack roll or saving "
"throw."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/bless.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**At Higher Levels.** When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd "
"level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level "
"above 1st. \n"
msgstr ""
